net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.util

Class DDUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dragondelve.customdriversutil.util.DDUtil

  • public class DDUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    General Utility class that provides some useful static values for default file locations. Non instatiable. in order to retrieve its only instance use getInstance.
